  "texts": [
    "However, ENMA's model's cost increases with respect to the number of latent tokens per state.",
    "This motivates future work on adaptive generation strategies-for instance, using a coarse-to-fine decoding scheme where a token directly synthesizes the frame, and remaining tokens act as refinements (Bachmann et al., 2025).",
    "Broader impact PDE solvers are key to applications in weather, climate, medicine, aerodynamics, and defense.",
    "While ENMA is not deployed in such settings, it offers fast, uncertainty-aware surrogates adaptable to new regimes.",
    "We summarize the main notations used throughout the paper:"
  ]
